______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
|
|
|                PROGRAM: abunfit.py
|
|                SYNOPSIS: ./abunfit_dual.py [input_file] [number_of_models] [alpha] [SNe_model_1] [SNe_model_2] ... 
|
|                DESCRIPTION: Fits a set of intra-cluster abundances with a combination of 
|                supernova (SNe) yield models. Several models (either SNcc or SNIa) are available 
|                and can be updated or created.
|
|                ARGUMENTS: 
|
|                        [input_file] -- (Location of the) Text input file of the set of measured  
|                                        ICM abundances. This file must contain 3 columns:  
|                                        (1) the element number (Z), 
|                                        (2) the measured abundance, and 
|                                        (3) its associated (symmetrical) uncertainties.
|
|                        [number_of_models] -- Integer (from 1 to 4) indicating the number of 
|                                              models to be fitted simultaneously (min: 1, max: 4).
|                        [alpha] -- Slope index of the assumed initial mass function (IMF). 
|                                   E.g.: for Salpeter IMF, alpha = -2.35.
|                        [model<1/2/...>] -- Name of the model. Currently available models: 
|                                            ==============
|                                            ==== SNIa ====
|                                            ==============
|                                            == Iwamoto et al. (1999)
|                                             - Iwamoto_W7
|                                             - Iwamoto_W70
|                                             - Iwamoto_WDD1
|                                             - Iwamoto_WDD2
|                                             - Iwamoto_WDD3
|                                             - Iwamoto_CDD1
|                                             - Iwamoto_CDD2
|                                            == Badenes et al. (2006)
|                                               (Based on Tycho's best spectral fits...)
|                                             - Badenes_DDTa
|                                             - Badenes_DDTb
|                                             - Badenes_DDTc
|                                             - Badenes_DDTd
|                                             - Badenes_DDTe
|                                             - Badenes_DDTf
|                                            == Maeda et al. (2010)
|                                               (2-D explosion models...)
|                                             - Maeda_C-DEF
|                                             - Maeda_C-DDT
|                                             - Maeda_O-DDT
|                                            == Seitenzahl et al. (2013)
|                                               (3-D delayed-detonation explosion models...)
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N1
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N3
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N5
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N10
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N20
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N40
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N100H
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N100
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N100L
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N150
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N200
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N300C
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N1600
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N1600C
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N100_Z0.5
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N100_Z0.1
|                                             - Seitenzahl_N100_Z0.01
|                                            == Fink et al. (2014)
|                                               (3-D deflagration explosion models...)
|                                             - Fink_N1def
|                                             - Fink_N3def
|                                             - Fink_N5def
|                                             - Fink_N10def
|                                             - Fink_N20def
|                                             - Fink_N40def
|                                             - Fink_N100Hdef
|                                             - Fink_N100def
|                                             - Fink_N100Ldef
|                                             - Fink_N150def
|                                             - Fink_N200def
|                                             - Fink_N300Cdef
|                                             - Fink_N1600def
|                                             - Fink_N1600Cdef
|                                            ==== Ca-rich gap transient SNe ====
|                                            == Waldman et al. (2011)
|                                             - Waldman_CO.45HE.2
|                                             - Waldman_CO.55HE.2
|                                             - Waldman_CO.5HE.15
|                                             - Waldman_CO.5HE.2
|                                             - Waldman_CO.5HE.2C.3
|                                             - Waldman_CO.5HE.2N.02
|                                             - Waldman_CO.5HE.3
|                                             - Waldman_CO.6HE.2
|                                            ==== Sub-Chandrasekhar DD merger ====
|                                            == Pakmor et al. (2010)
|                                             - Pakmor
|                                            ==============
|                                            ==== SNcc ====
|                                            ==============
|                                            == Chieffi & Limongi (2004)
|                                               (One initial metallicity per model...)
|                                             - Chieffi_0
|                                             - Chieffi_1E-6
|                                             - Chieffi_1E-4
|                                             - Chieffi_1E-3
|                                             - Chieffi_6E-3
|                                             - Chieffi_2E-2
|                                            == Nomoto et al. (2006)
|                                               (One initial metallicity per model...)
|                                             - Nomoto_0
|                                             - Nomoto_0.001
|                                             - Nomoto_0.004
|                                             - Nomoto_0.02
|                                            == Nomoto et al. (2013)
|                                               (One initial metallicity per model...)
|                                             = SNcc: 11 - 40 (140) M_sun
|                                              - N13_SNcc_0
|                                              - N13_SNcc_0.001
|                                              - N13_SNcc_0.004
|                                              - N13_SNcc_0.008
|                                              - N13_SNcc_0.02
|                                              - N13_SNcc_0.05
|                                             = PISNe: 140 - 300 M_sun
|                                              - N13_PISNe_0
|                                             = All SNe (SNcc+PISNe): 11 - 300 M_sun
|                                              - N13_SNe_0
|                                             = HNe: 20 - 40 (140) M_sun
|                                              - N13_HNe_0
|                                              - N13_HNe_0.001
|                                              - N13_HNe_0.004
|                                              - N13_HNe_0.008
|                                              - N13_HNe_0.02
|                                              - N13_HNe_0.05
|                                            == Heger & Woosley (2002,2010)
|                                               (Initial metallicity always 0!)
|                                             = SNcc: 10 - 100 M_sun
|                                              - HW_SNcc_0
|                                             = PISNe: 140 - 260 M_sun
|                                              - HW_PISNe_0
|                                             = All SNe (SNcc+PISNe): 10 - 260 M_sun
|                                              - HW_SNe_0
|                                            ===================
|                                            ==== AGB stars ====
|                                            ===================
|                                            == Nomoto et al. (2013)
|                                               (One initial metallicity per model...)
|                                             = AGB: 0.9 - 6.5 M_sun (adapted from Karakas 2010)
|                                             = THE AGB MODEL MUST AT THE FIRST POSITION!
|                                              - N13_AGB+SNcc_0
|                                              - N13_AGB+SNcc_0.001
|                                              - N13_AGB+SNcc_0.004
|                                              - N13_AGB+SNcc_0.008
|                                              - N13_AGB+SNcc_0.02
|
|                EXAMPLE: ./abunfit.py cluster/average_CHEERS.out 2 -2.35 Iwamoto_WDD2 Nomoto_0.02
